{"tid":319133,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇養貓巴打有買貓香薰","createTime":"2017-07-12T14:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T04:08:53.000Z","uid":30807,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65a7b6d5ad7e58b3796204c400e45d6207435af3","tid":319133,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"屋企隻新貓b入屋兩星期，兩個月大，小小聲就嚇到成隻彈起。<br />\n好少見到佢訓覺。明明咁細隻應該訓好耐。<br />\n<br />\n想試下貓香薰掂唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢唔驚人但係又對聲音好敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l8nbp6ik\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl8nbp6ik&h=952d6890&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67feae6982d396fd445e1abc41a99a39f1617ed4","tid":319133,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b5dsei4q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb5dsei4q&h=2083c6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個月"},{"pid":"3dc6d83f177a6f7d5e1f2a4abc247689488a49ef","tid":319133,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"feliway? 用左一個月 冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係隻隻貓都有用<br />\n我個次就係趕住用 去左太平道買 成570蚊一set<br />\n之後上網見到好似有代購300蚊set<br />\n但用落真係冇乜大分別"},{"pid":"528031a9ebbc495076bc02d4d47c756519f0f67b","tid":319133,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>feliway? 用左一個月 冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係隻隻貓都有用<br />\n我個次就係趕住用 去左太平道買 成570蚊一set<br />\n之後上網見到好似有代購300蚊set<br />\n但用落真係冇乜大分別</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ok<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇聽過d有效既例子？"},{"pid":"8746